<div class="pa">
  <h1>Practice Areas</h1>

  <p>At VMG Business Advisory PLLC, I provide targeted legal services designed to support businesses, founders, funds, and investors through all stages of growth and transactions. My experience includes:</p>

  <div class="blocks">

    <div>
      <h3><a href="/practice-areas/corporate-governance/">Corporate Governance</a></h3>
      <p>Advising companies, boards, and executives on governance matters, fiduciary duties, corporate structure, and internal policies to ensure compliant and effective management.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h3><a href="/practice-areas/private-placements-securities/">Private Placements &amp; Securities</a></h3>
      <p>Structuring and documenting private offerings of securities, including early-stage equity rounds, convertible notes, SAFE instruments, and compliance with federal and state securities regulations.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h3><a href="/practice-areas/mergers-acquisitions/">Mergers &amp; Acquisitions</a></h3>
      <p>Handling business purchase and sale transactions, including asset purchases, stock sales, mergers, joint ventures, and complex negotiation of deal terms.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h3><a href="/practice-areas/venture-capital-safe-negotiation/">Venture Capital &amp; SAFE Negotiation</a></h3>
      <p>Counseling startup founders and venture investors in negotiating investment rounds, including seed, Series A, and later-stage financing transactions using SAFE agreements, convertible notes, or priced equity rounds.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h3><a href="/practice-areas/startup-counseling/">Start-Up Counseling</a></h3>
      <p>Providing strategic legal counsel to startups on entity formation, founder agreements, intellectual property protection, contract negotiation, and general business matters.</p>

      <p>Guiding companies through drafting and negotiating SAFE, convertible, and priced-equity instruments that balance investor flexibility with founder control, while advising on corporate governance, vesting structures, and cap-table modeling to clarify dilution scenarios and prepare for future rounds or acquisitions.</p>

      <p>Helping businesses explore practical and compliant ways to integrate AI tools into their operations, focusing on efficiency, risk awareness, and responsible adoption.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h3><a href="/practice-areas/professional-service-entities/">Professional Service Entities</a></h3>
      <p>Advising regulated professional service firms on entity formation, mergers and acquisitions, ongoing regulatory compliance, ownership structuring, and transactional matters specific to licensed professions.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h3><a href="/practice-areas/not-for-profit/">Not for Profit Entities</a></h3>
      <p>Advising nonprofit organizations on formation, governance, and compliance, helping founders and boards establish and maintain 501(c) exempt entities efficiently and lawfully.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h3><a href="/practice-areas/outside-general-counsel/">Outside General Counsel Services</a></h3>
      <p>Serving as trusted ongoing legal counsel to businesses without full-time in-house counsel, assisting with commercial contracts, employment matters, regulatory compliance, and day-to-day legal issues.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h3><a href="/practice-areas/nuclear-startup-advisory/">Nuclear Startup Advisory</a></h3>
      <p>Advising multiple small modular reactor (SMR) startups on corporate governance, equity structures, regulatory strategy, and venture financing.</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>
